THIRD-PARTY COMPONENTS

This repository bundles or builds on the following third-party components,
each under its own license. None of them are MIT-incompatible.

  tools/texconv.exe
    Microsoft DirectXTex — MIT
    https://github.com/microsoft/DirectXTex

  app/data/mapping.json, app/data/loc.json, app/data/taxonomy.json
    Derived from MBINCompiler-extracted NMS data (MIT)
    https://github.com/monkeyman192/MBINCompiler

  app/data/icons.json (manifest only — the PNG files are NOT bundled)
    Filenames and paths derived from MBINCompiler taxonomy data.

THIRD-PARTY COMPONENTS NOT INCLUDED IN THIS REPO

The following are required to use the icon-extraction feature but are not
shipped here. Users provide them via the setup wizard.

  hgpaktool.exe
    From AMUMSS (https://github.com/HolterPhylo/AMUMSS) or zencq/HGPak
    (https://github.com/zencq/HGPak). License: GPLv3.

  No Man's Sky game assets (.dds icon textures inside NMSARC.TexUI.pak)
    © Hello Games. Extracted locally from your own install for personal
    use only. Not redistributed.
